The controversial singer is trending on Twitter after he shared a video where he confessed to be the leader of One Million Boys cult.
In the Video, Portable was heard bragging about how he and his guys usually shake things in their area. In the now deleted video, Portable made it known that he is not scared of anyone and he is ready to fight anyone who drag him for supporting APC.
Nigerians have take to Twitter and Instagram to plead with Olamide, Obi Cubana and others to drop Portable. According to them, portable is a negative influence to their brand and they should dump him immediately.






